# L1-5b: Simple 90-degree PEC wedge — UTD diffraction test
# 0-face: x=2 plane, y>0, normal=(-1,0,0) pointing toward -X (exterior)
# N-face: y=2 plane, x>0, normal=(0,-1,0) pointing toward -Y (exterior)
# Shared edge: (2,2,-10) to (2,2,10), direction=(0,0,1)
# Wedge interior: x>2 AND y>2 (exterior is the region outside this quadrant)
o face0
v 2.0 2.0 -10.0
v 2.0 10.0 -10.0
v 2.0 10.0 10.0
v 2.0 2.0 10.0
vn -1.0 0.0 0.0
f 1//1 2//1 3//1
f 1//1 3//1 4//1

o faceN
v 2.0 2.0 -10.0
v 10.0 2.0 -10.0
v 10.0 2.0 10.0
v 2.0 2.0 10.0
vn 0.0 -1.0 0.0
f 5//2 7//2 6//2
f 6//2 7//2 8//2
